```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant C as Client
  participant A as Caller Service
  participant CB as Circuit Breaker
  participant D as Downstream

  C->>A: GET /proxy/data
  A->>CB: check state
  alt CB OPEN
    CB-->>A: fail-fast
    A-->>C: 200 fallback (degraded)
  else CB CLOSED/HALF_OPEN
    loop up to N retries with backoff+jitter
      A->>D: GET /data (timeout)
      alt transient failure/timeout
        D-->>A: 5xx/timeout
        A->>A: wait backoff + jitter
      else success
        D-->>A: 200 OK
        A-->>C: 200 OK
      end
    end
    alt retries exhausted
      A-->>C: 200 fallback (or 503)
    end
  end
```
